{"tid":6074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不想搭下班車　大媽抬輪椅上港鐵","createTime":"2016-11-27T07:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T08:12:54.000Z","uid":19502,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56ac60cd94cee8ff4079d1603ad4c85b851b3567","tid":6074,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:26:37.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=clALeOvgxUNRb4a8GJIPAsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=60eadbb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】港鐵為便利坐輪椅人士，會派職員協助他們上落車。網上近日流傳一條短片，片中坐着輪椅的大媽，不滿港鐵職員未能即時安排協助上車，趕時間下，她竟站起並離開輪椅，再自行抬輪椅車登上列車。 <br />\n<br />\n短片於港鐵列車車廂拍攝，當時列車正在關門，並駛離月台，門前則有一名港鐵職員，以及一名正在推着輪椅的大媽。拍片者指出，該名女士是水貨大媽，她在月台等車時，港職職員要求她上下一班列車，以便安排職員在她落車站提供協助，但大媽拒絕，「輪椅客竟起身擋住正關閉的車門來抬輪椅上車，再投訴港鐵職員。」片中只見大媽抬輪椅上車後，將輪椅推到車廂中心，然後坐下，並以不純正的廣東話向職員質問：「點解要我搭下一架呢？」 <br />\n<br />\n網友睇片後，指是怒氣沖天下即時康復，「激到企返起身？」，「行得返咁勁？咁仲唔多謝職員？」也有網友指若該大媽是使用港鐵推出的殘疾人士車費推廣計劃，則可能涉及呃車資，「扮跛騙2元乘車優惠」、「香港有好多扮傷殘人士呃人」、「真傷殘，會有傷殘證的」。<br />\n <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161126/bkn-20161126185527165-1126_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161126%2Fbkn-20161126185527165-1126_00822_001.html&d=clALeOvgxUNRb4a8GJIPAsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=141cd77e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161126/bkn-20161126185527165-1126_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/152541_1d7335ae175d974596f5642bdb843d11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F152541_1d7335ae175d974596f5642bdb843d11.jpg&h=7cbcb5d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0aa125135b5968023e933e2d517a302f0a9eb3c","tid":6074,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"又係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d9ab78b52638c59fe9c64c4be6e1d978fe3dcf","tid":6074,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:28:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蝗大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb91cbfd6d87797d3bdd0417b2292d5a929bfb7","tid":6074,"uid":25002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:29:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a258e74f30b49e99f93008b46dc956eea1b87e1d","tid":6074,"uid":25002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:29:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29eb86bcf5c1465d792c983f13cbbc70a8e5637d","tid":6074,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>條大媽有手有腳就咪𠹌坐輪椅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔坐輪椅就無得用傷殘優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd12d6b10b2deaa781d6562551c67407b63fab5","tid":6074,"uid":19067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:33:08.000Z","msg":"坐輪椅過關多數海關唔check <br />\n走大量水貨都冇人理"},{"pid":"742e43ec684f1465eef56dbe351c37b7998d3e32","tid":6074,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"其實呢d咪香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講道理再投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經對香港人無好感"},{"pid":"d33e8603352f3bade4e62d8e73b7906bce5dd7e2","tid":6074,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢d咪香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講道理再投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經對香港人無好感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不純正既廣東話喎大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":